  <summary date="2019-08-29T14:29:16Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Iran Hostage Act

This bill imposes sanctions on Iranian persons who&#160;are responsible for politically-motivated harassment, abuse, extortion, arrest, trial, conviction, sentencing, or imprisonment of U.S. citizens or lawful permanent resident aliens with significant ties to the United States, regardless of whether such actions occurred in Iran.</summary>
